gipsec
===========

This project provide the GUI to configure the server and client mode of
ipsec-tools, monitor the connection traffic and view the connection log.
Also it provide a text graphic interface could be used in terminal.

This package provides a way to use the native IPsec functionality 
in the Linux 2.6+ kernel.

Sources can be found at the gipsec home page at:
	http://code.google.com/p/gipsec/
Also you can reports bugs in issues page, and view project wiki in wiki page.

And SVN repository is hosted at google code:
	svn checkout http://gipsec.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ gipsec-read-only

Credits:
	ipsec-tools, see http://ipsec-tools.sourceforge.net/
	SUSE Linux, see http://www.novell.com/
